@startuml pipeline-ports
' Interface design — pass 1: pipeline stage ports.
' The four traits live in librarian-domain. Adapters outside the domain
' implement them. Every stage : AdapterIdentity (name / version /
' config_hash) — used by the runner to derive CacheKey.

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName "Helvetica"
skinparam ArrowColor #444

package "librarian-domain" {
  interface Extractor
  interface Chunker
  interface Embedder
  interface Indexer

  Extractor -right-> Chunker  : ExtractedText
  Chunker   -right-> Embedder : Vec<Chunk>
  Embedder  -right-> Indexer  : Vec<Vector>

  note top of Extractor : extract(Document)\n-> ExtractedText
  note top of Chunker   : chunk(ExtractedText)\n-> Vec<Chunk>
  note top of Embedder  : embed(&[ChunkText])\n-> Vec<Vector>\nError: Recoverable | Terminal
  note top of Indexer   : upsert / replace /\ndelete_by_source_id
}

note bottom : All four : **AdapterIdentity** — name() / version() / config_hash()\nAdapter crates outside librarian-domain provide the implementations.

@enduml
